responsibilities:
- data collection and analysis using sql and python.
- process, cleanse, and verify the integrity of data used for analysis.
- interpret data, analyse results using statistical techniques, identify trends or patterns in complex data sets, and provide analytics reports to drive business insights.
- develop new reports and dashboards to help users make faster and better decisions.
 
requirements: 
- pursuing undergraduate or graduate degree in math, statistics, engineering, computer science or related field.
- able to commit part-time, min 3 working days a week (full-time preferred) internship during 3 or 6 month.
